@startuml
title Activity, Summary, and Leaderboard
hide footbox
autonumber

skinparam BackgroundColor transparent
skinparam SequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam MaxMessageSize 110
skinparam WrapWidth 220
skinparam RoundCorner 8

actor "Host browser\nstatic/host.js" as Host
actor "Participant browser\nstatic/participant.js" as Participant
participant "Daemon activity router" as ActivityAPI
participant "Daemon participant state router" as ParticipantStateAPI
participant "Daemon main loop\nsummary probe" as Loop
database "Session folder\nai-summary.md + notes" as SessionFiles
participant "Daemon summary / misc APIs" as SummaryAPI
participant "Daemon leaderboard router" as LeaderboardAPI
participant "Railway session WS" as RailwayWS

group Activity switching
Host -> ActivityAPI: POST /host/activity {activity}
ActivityAPI -> ActivityAPI: set participant_state.current_activity
ActivityAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast activity_updated
RailwayWS --> Participant: activity_updated
Participant -> ParticipantStateAPI: refresh /api/participant/state\nwhen stateful activity changes
ParticipantStateAPI --> Participant: full personalised state payload
RailwayWS --> Host: activity_updated
end

group Summary counts and modal fetch
Loop -> SessionFiles: poll notes + ai-summary.md metadata
alt Notes or summary counts changed
  Loop -> RailwayWS: broadcast notes_updated
  Loop -> RailwayWS: broadcast summary_updated
end

Host -> SummaryAPI: GET /host/summary
SummaryAPI -> SessionFiles: read ai-summary.md via read_summary_payload()
SummaryAPI --> Host: points + updated_at

Participant -> SummaryAPI: GET /api/participant/summary
SummaryAPI -> SessionFiles: read ai-summary.md via read_summary_payload()
SummaryAPI --> Participant: points + raw_markdown + updated_at
end

group Leaderboard reveal / hide
Host -> LeaderboardAPI: POST /host/leaderboard/show
LeaderboardAPI -> LeaderboardAPI: compute top positive scores\nstore leaderboard_state
LeaderboardAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast leaderboard_revealed
RailwayWS --> Host: reveal top 5 overlay
RailwayWS --> Participant: reveal leaderboard + personal rank

Host -> LeaderboardAPI: POST /host/leaderboard/hide
LeaderboardAPI -> LeaderboardAPI: clear leaderboard_state
LeaderboardAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast leaderboard_hidden
end
@enduml
